without a reason.

270
00:24:29,342 --> 00:24:30,552
What are you trying to do?

271
00:24:30,677 --> 00:24:32,554
Just give me that yukgaejang!

272
00:24:32,846 --> 00:24:33,972
This is incredible.

273
00:24:35,182 --> 00:24:36,975
