-Who made him like that?

312
00:27:17,135 --> 00:27:21,222
My gosh. You're so old-fashioned.

313
00:27:21,681 --> 00:27:24,642
Celebrities aren't treated awfully
like in the old days.

314
00:27:24,809 --> 00:27:27,562
