she should give me some yukgaejang?

326
00:28:10,188 --> 00:28:12,357
I won't give you a bite. This is all mine.

327
00:28:12,482 --> 00:28:15,026
Why are you refusing
to do this documentary?

328
00:28:15,193 --> 00:28:16,569
