387
00:31:50,074 --> 00:31:51,492
Am I wrong?

388
00:31:52,035 --> 00:31:53,703
Hey, are you crazy?

389
00:31:54,704 --> 00:31:55,663
You too.

390
00:31:56,539 --> 00:31:59,083
You covered up Yuil Motors'
supplier corruption

391
00:31:59,292 --> 00:32:03,296
